BlackBerry backup/restore and GPRS modem access

Requires:
 * OpenMotif, theres a SlackBuild submitted, also found at http://batts.mine.nu/pub/src/SlackBuilds/openmotif/
 * Xlt, theres a SlackBuild submitted, also found at http://batts.mine.nu/pub/src/SlackBuilds/xlt/
 * libusb, by default included in the Slackware full install
 * opensync (optional for attempting synchronization)
